{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLightnessLinearSet\/delay","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh23LightLightnessLinearSetV5delays5UInt8VSgvp","title":"delay","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLightnessLinearSet"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file has to be set together with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lightlightnesslinearset\/delay"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/transitionTime":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/transitiontime","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Transition Time field identifies the time that an Element will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"take to transition to the target state from the present state."}],"required":true,"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transitionTime"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TransitionTime","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh14TransitionTimeV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"transitionTime"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightLightnessLinearSet":{"abstract":[],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LightLightnessLinearSet"}],"title":"LightLightnessLinearSet","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/ligh